            "id": 5898881,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數下跌-175.44點至5669.92點，跌幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間13日01:34，恆生科技指數下跌175.44點（或3%），暫報5669.92點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.52%</li><li>近 1 月：+10.68%</li><li>近 3 月：+27.05%</li><li>近 6 月：+68.2%</li><li>今年以來：+30.82%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>醫療保健設備概念領跌-3.57%。其中    啓明醫療－Ｂ(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02500:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02500\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02500-HK</a>)            下跌        61.03%            ;        巨星醫療控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02393:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02393\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02393-HK</a>)            下跌        7.89%            ;        沛嘉醫療－Ｂ(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09996:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09996\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09996-HK</a>)            下跌        3.42%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>林業及木材概念領跌-2.89%。其中    信保環球控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00723:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00723\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00723-HK</a>)            下跌        9.09%            ;        綠心集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00094:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00094\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00094-HK</a>)            下跌        7.69%            ;        中國健康科技集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01069:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01069\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01069-HK</a>)            下跌        7.5%    。</p></section></main>",
